3. cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper proposes an indoor navigation and positioning algorithm, which may involve machine learning techniques. 
4. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture): The paper discusses the use of optical camera communication for indoor navigation, which may involve networking and internet architecture.
